{"tid":599263,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[真男人] 做得出唔怕認 嫖賭飲吹你中幾樣？","createTime":"2018-03-20T08:57:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T11:35:48.000Z","uid":10249,"like":95,"dislike":847,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"d101bb69bcbf6e75f3c5f19f839ae55a2870e400","tid":599263,"uid":10249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T08:57:18.000Z","msg":"我懺悔先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嫖 - 未結婚前 人K 㩒鐘仔 桑拿乜都玩 結婚後有過兩段婚外情 宜家有個SP<br />\n<br />\n賭 - 自細已經有賭波 呢幾年學埋賭馬 波都叫和和地 馬仔只有出無入 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n飲 - 無酒不歡 一個禮拜4晚hh再直落 平時行行下街都會買啤酒飲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n吹 - 大學時有隊草 煙無食 因為覺得好臭 同埋似慢性自殺<br />\n<br />\n順便做個統計 <br />\n中三樣或以上既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中兩樣或以下既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d550e15f4935001e6176db836af34433e8b13bd7","tid":599263,"uid":127177,"like":16,"dislike":4,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T09:01:22.000Z","msg":"你都幾有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bbc56540f4e90dc123c3cd806e7dead51a25a8c","tid":599263,"uid":10249,"like":62,"dislike":10,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T09:04:02.000Z","msg":"開呢個post係因為早兩日同班friend傾偈 (有男有女）<br />\n班仔個個話自己中晒三四樣 班女個個話自己老公/男友係好好仔 最多食下煙飲下酒 一定唔會嫖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地班仔覺得啲女真係好天真好傻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdedda3f7ec9c99389efeead48b62e3425e8776c","tid":599263,"uid":105445,"like":51,"dislike":7,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T09:04:02.000Z","msg":"剩係嫖 玩過唔少女 都算不枉此生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4e671f91c37f1bc24cd06a6f03316a5668ec8b","tid":599263,"uid"